actionConfiguration.body:

    public."TimeAttackRecord" AS t
    JOIN public."Car" AS c ON t."carId" = c."carId"

		JOIN public."Car" AS car2 ON t."carId" = car2."carId"
WHERE
    t.course = {{SelectTrack.selectedOptionValue}};
SELECT pg_sleep(3);
